CRITICAL GAP found in audit. The admin frontend (createEntityApi.ts) sends sort as JSON.stringify([{id, desc}]) but AdminSearchBaseSchema validates with regex /^[a-zA-Z_]+:(asc|desc)$/. All admin sorting is silently broken.

Fix in apps/admin/src/components/entity-list/api/createEntityApi.ts lines 58-60:

Change:
```ts
if (sort && sort.length > 0) {
    params.set('sort', JSON.stringify(sort));
}
```
To:
```ts
if (sort && sort.length > 0) {
    const [firstSort] = sort;
    if (firstSort) {
        const direction = firstSort.desc ? 'desc' : 'asc';
        params.set('sort', `${firstSort.id}:${direction}`);
    }
}
```

